		<title>이번주에 상승이 전망되는 항셍 인덱스</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/ko/analysis/market-news/hang-seng-stock-index-rally-this-week</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 31 Jul 2023 08:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[마켓 뉴스 및 자료]]></category>
